@startuml

title E Visa Processing And Follow Up System State Transition Diagram

initial : Initial State

state "Logged Out" {}
state "Logged In" {}
state "Account Created" {}
state "Application Applied" {}
state "Status Viewed" {}
state "Feedback Given" {}
state "Details Modified" {}
state "Details Viewed" {}
state "Cancelled Application" {}
state "Final State" {}

Logged Out --> Account Created : Create Account
Account Created --> Logged In : Log In
Logged In --> Application Applied : Apply For Visa, Make Payment, Accept Application
Application Applied --> Status Viewed : View Status
Status Viewed --> Status Viewed : Check Status
Status Viewed --> Feedback Given : Give Feedback
Feedback Given --> Details Modified : Modify Details
Details Modified --> Details Viewed : View Details
Details Viewed --> Final State : Log Out
Logged In --> Cancelled Application : Cancel Application

@enduml
